{"pageProps":{"postContent":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"I changed the content hosting of this blog from notion (notion API) to markdown files.","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":261},"end":{"line":12,"column":87,"offset":347}}}]},{"type":"heading","depth":1,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Motivations","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":3,"offset":351},"end":{"line":14,"column":14,"offset":362}}}]},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Notion API limit","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":4,"offset":366},"end":{"line":15,"column":20,"offset":382}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Some of the image links returned from the notion API only work for one hour. This is a spec. I can workaround it but it feels like a hustle.","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":384},"end":{"line":16,"column":141,"offset":524}}}]},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mind integration with ","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":4,"offset":529},"end":{"line":18,"column":26,"offset":551}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://obsidian.md","children":[{"type":"text","value":"obsidian.md","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":27,"offset":552},"end":{"line":18,"column":38,"offset":563}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":26,"offset":551},"end":{"line":18,"column":60,"offset":585}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"I've been heavily using obsidian lately. The notes helps me writing blog posts immensely. Some posts wrote themselves. This very post was wrote on obsidian too. I figured it's easier to write and publish the markdown files directly.","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1,"offset":586},"end":{"line":19,"column":233,"offset":818}}}]},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I own my data","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":4,"offset":823},"end":{"line":21,"column":17,"offset":836}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Most of my data are stored on somebody's server. And I either am okay with that or do not care that much. But the notes and blog posts are very personal things, so personal that I stopped entirely trusting some companies and store all my posts there. I wanted to make sure that if for some reason all my accounts are not accessible anymore, I still have all my posts.","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1,"offset":837},"end":{"line":22,"column":368,"offset":1204}}}]},{"type":"heading","depth":1,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stacks","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":3,"offset":1208},"end":{"line":24,"column":9,"offset":1214}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Markdown parser: ","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1,"offset":1215},"end":{"line":25,"column":18,"offset":1232}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://remark.js.org/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"remark","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":19,"offset":1233},"end":{"line":25,"column":25,"offset":1239}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":18,"offset":1232},"end":{"line":25,"column":50,"offset":1264}}},{"type":"text","value":"\nFrontmatter parser: selfmade","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":50,"offset":1264},"end":{"line":26,"column":29,"offset":1293}}}]}],"postSummary":{"id":"refactor-blog-2023-markdown-based-content","title":"Refactor Blog 2023: Markdown Based Content","category":"Meta","language":["en-US"],"tags":[],"publishDate":"2023-06-19","pathname":"refactor-blog-2023-markdown-based-content","zhTwLink":null,"filename":"Refactor Blog 2023 - Markdown Based Content (blog)"}},"__N_SSG":true}